<i>Epizoda 14</i>

7
00:00:34,750 --> 00:00:36,580
Co to děláš?

8
00:00:38,010 --> 00:00:39,560
Co to...

9
00:00:42,380 --> 00:00:44,300
Omlouvám se.

10
